#
# T3_jlmb_proton_elastic
#
# TALYS JLMB (jlmmode 0, default) proton elastic scattering on 120Sn at Ep = 10 MeV.
# Tests the Coulomb pathway: jitr must supply density-derived Coulomb to both
# the JLM delta_C correction and workspace.xs(coulomb_potential=...).
# jlmmode defaults to 0 (alam = 0.44, Eq. 11.47 standard).
#
projectile p
element    sn
mass       120
energy     T3_jlmb_proton_elastic.energies
jlmomp y
outangle y
fileelastic y
